description:
**The job in short**
 Together with your team you will maintain and extend our mobile product offering. Are you ready to take our mobile apps to the next level?




**Meet the job**
 Developers all over the world will use your code when developing state\\-of\\-the\\-art mobile apps for the fintech industry. That’s why you will constantly create stunning products with remarkable user experience.




 As you know, mobile banking trends are constantly changing. It’s your job to adapt to these changes and see into the future. You enjoy coming up with innovative features and turning them into new tools for our customers. Our product is never finished. Are you up for the challenge?




**What about you?**
* You’ve earned your stripes designing and building Android apps, and at least one can be found on Google Play;
* Your friends would define you as the “getting things done” type;
* The Agile philosophy is your lifestyle;
* We won’t have to tell you anything about mobile development for Android. You’ll be the one teaching us your best practices;
* An additional bonus for us would be your experience with testing frameworks (JUnit, Mockito, Espresso), scripting languages (Gradle, Groovy, Python), and/or Jenkins.
